content.rendered: Pusat mesin absensi sidik jari ZKTECO, kami menyediakan fingerprint Akses Control ZKTECO MB2000 untuk anda dengan harga murah. Mesin absensi sidik jari ZKTECO dapat menangkap rekam sidik jari untuk karyawan dalam jumlah banyak. Jenis fingerprint ZKTECO type Akses Control ZKTECO MB2000 memiliki spesifikasi, yaitu: Face Capacity: 2,000 Fingerprint Capacity: 3,000 ID Card Capacity : 3,000 Algorithm: ZKFinger 10.0/ ZKFace 7.0100,000 User: 3,000 Record Capacity: 100,000 Display: 2.8-inch TFT Screen Communication: TCP/IP，USB-Host，Wi-Fi(Optional) Standard Functions: Work Code, SMS, DST, Scheduled-bell, Self-Service Query, Automatic Status Switch, Photo ID T9 Input, Camera, 9 digit user ID, Built-in Battery, Multiple Verify Mode, External Bell Access Control Interface for : Lock, Door Sensor, Exit Button, Alarm Optional Functions : ID/MF, WDMS Power Supply: DC 12V 1.5A Operating Temp: 0 °C – 45 °C Operating Humidity: 20%-80% Dimension: 180 x 154 x 34.2 mm
